rjpres - Reveal-JS Presenter
============================

Provides convenient way to run Reveal-JS on local machine
by providing all the necessary JavaScript and CSS files
from the install of the rjpres modules

INSTALL
-------

   easy_install rjpres

rjpres is listed in `PyPI
<http://pypi.python.org/pypi/rjpres>`_ and can be installed with 
``pip`` or ``easy_install``. 

RUN
---

In some directory where you have a markdown (.md) file that will
be your presentation:

   rjp

and then access as <http://localhost:9999>.
